Tadelech Bekele (amụrụ na ụbọsị iri na otu n'ọnwa Eprel n'afọ 1991) bụ onye Etiopia na-agba ọsọ ogologo oge.
Na afọ 2012, o meriri České Budějovice Half Marathon na oge nke 1:10:54
N'afọ a, o merikwara Prague Grand Prix na oge nke 15:48, afọ ikpeazụ Prague Grand Prix bụ ọsọ kilomita ise maka ụmụ nwaanyị.

Na afọ 2014, o meriri Berlin Half Marathon na oge nke 1:10:05.
N'afọ 2017 na 2018 ọ meriri na Amsterdam Marathon
Na Berlin Marathon ọ gwụchara n'ọnọdụ nke anọ na 2014 Berlin Marathon na 2015 Berlin Marathon.
Na 2018 London Marathon ọ gwụchara n'ọnọdụ nke atọ na oge nke 2:21:40.
